 * Commands:
 *   /xpert              → Interactive team browser: select team → activate/deactivate
 *   /xpert on <team>    → Activate a team (enable all its agents)
 *   /xpert off <team>   → Deactivate a team (disable all its agents)
 *   /xpert toggle <prefix> → Toggle all agents with prefix (e.g., "res-phd")
 *   /xpert status       → Show all teams and their current activation status
